              <li><a href="/docs/vision/open-source/">Open source commitment</a></li>
              <li><a href="/docs/vision/non-goals/">Non-goals and tradeoffs</a></li>
              <li><a href="/docs/vision/benchmarks/">Benchmarks</a></li>
            </ul>

