            <p>beava is early, and we want to build it with people who feel this problem directly.</p>
            <p>Try it locally, read the public RFCs, join the weekly dev call, or catch up through summaries from previous calls.</p>
            <p>Help us make <strong>real-time features feel like application code</strong>.</p>

